<title>rby ạ̉nt tstṭyʿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- rby ạ̉nt tstṭyʿ kl sẖyʾiⁿ .. lys sẖyʾ gẖyr mstṭạʿiⁿ ldyk
 kl sẖyʾiⁿ kl sẖyʾiⁿ .. kl sẖyʾiⁿ mstṭạʿuⁿ ldyk
 1- (ʿnd ktẖrẗ hmwmy wậlạmy .. ʿndmạ ạ̉ry̱ ạlạ̉bwạb twṣd ạ̉mạmy)2
 ạ̉nt wḥdk ạ̉nt wḥdk .. ạ̉nt wḥdk tftḥ ạlạ̉bwạb
 2- (fy ṣlybk fdạỷy wʿzạỷy .. fy ṣlybk ạ̉ry̱ ạldwạʾ ldạỷy)2
 ạ̉nt wḥdk ạ̉nt wḥdk .. ạ̉nt wḥdk ly nbʿ ʿzạỷy</lyrics>
</song>